DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());

$g = random(2,9,1);

BEGIN_TEXT

A Cartesian equation for the polar equation \(r=$g \) can be written as:
$BR$BR
\( x^2+y^2 =\) \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
END_TEXT

$ans = "$g*$g";
ANS(num_cmp($ans));



ENDDOCUMENT();
